# Third-Party Licences

This file lists every crate `epd-dither` links against, grouped by
licence, with the verbatim upstream licence text. Generated by
`cargo about generate -c licensing/about.toml -o THIRD_PARTY_LICENSES.md licensing/about.hbs`;
re-run after a dependency change.

For `epd-dither`'s own licence see [LICENSE](./LICENSE); for the
bundled blue-noise tile, [NOTICE](./NOTICE).

